## Description {#details}

This structure holds any data we need about the edges being traversed during buildTree&#95;rec().

We keep track of: (i) the user TreeEntry index, and (ii) the index of the edge.

Definition at line 1660 of file <a href="/docs/api/files/lib/lib/transforms/lib/transforms/vectorize/slpvectorizer-cpp">SLPVectorizer.cpp</a>.
